    ],
    aiIntroductionTemplate: `Milestone miss hua. Okay. Ab sabse zaruri cheez: WHY? Kal ke liye ek diagnosis karenge aur fir naya, achievable target set karenge. Quit nahi karna — recalibrate karna hai.`,
    consistencyImpact: -5,
  },
